{"id": "art-1532", "label": "Art. 1532", "title": "Art. 1532", "slug": "art-1532", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_644115155\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2138\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_644115155\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153<sup>2</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1989999506\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2137\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1989999506\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Desemnarea membrilor directoratului revine consiliului\nde supraveghere, care atribuie totodat&#259; unuia dintre ei <span\nclass=SpellE>func&#355;ia</span> de <span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edinte</span>\nal directoratului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_400586083\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2136\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_400586083\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Actul constitutiv determin&#259; durata mandatului\ndirectoratului, în limitele prev&#259;zute la art. 153<sup>12</sup>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_289995966\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2135\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_289995966\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Membrii directoratului nu pot fi concomitent membri ai\nconsiliului de supraveghere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_547002099\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2134\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_547002099\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Membrii directoratului pot fi <span class=SpellE>revoca&#355;i</span>\noricând de c&#259;tre consiliul de supraveghere. Actul constitutiv poate\nprevedea c&#259; ei pot fi <span class=SpellE>revoca&#355;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de c&#259;tre adunarea general&#259; ordinar&#259;\na <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>. Dac&#259; revocarea lor survine\nf&#259;r&#259; just&#259; cauz&#259;, membrii directoratului sunt <span\nclass=SpellE>îndrept&#259;&#355;i&#355;i</span> la plata unor daune-interese.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_544745166\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2133\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_544745166\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)În caz de <span class=SpellE>vacan&#355;&#259;</span> a\nunui post de membru al directoratului, consiliul de supraveghere va proceda\nf&#259;r&#259; întârziere la desemnarea unui nou membru, pe durata\nr&#259;mas&#259; pân&#259; la expirarea mandatului directoratului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1651449911\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2132\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1651449911\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Cu privire la drepturile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n<span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span> membrilor directoratului, art. 137<sup>1</sup>\nalin. (3), art. 144<sup>1</sup>, art. 144<sup>2</sup>alin. (1), (4) <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> (5), art. 144<sup>3</sup>, art. 144<sup>4</sup>,\nart. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>150</span><span style='color:black'> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>152</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}